## Code Writing Principles

Before defining new components, utility functions, or types, always check if existing shared code can be reused.

If a request is better handled on the backend, do not modify any code yet — instead, suggest to me that it would be better to handle it on the backend first, and wait for my confirmation.

## Project Structure

hooks/
- Contains reusable logic wrapped as React hooks for components
- Wraps data fetching and mutations with useQuery and useMutation for direct UI consumption
- e.g. use-posts, use-categories

lib/
- Common utilities, storage, and environment logic independent of UI
- e.g. lib/i18n/*(i18n), lib/auth-atoms.ts(Jotai state), lib/storage.tsx, lib/utils.ts